				</div>
				<p class="cv-title">Full Stack Developer</p>
			</header>

			<div class="cv-body">
				<!-- LEFT COLUMN -->
				<aside class="cv-sidebar" aria-label="Personal information">

					<section class="cv-section">
						<h2 class="cv-section-title">Profile</h2>
						<p class="cv-profile-text">
							Currently in the final year of a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science at IUT of Bayonne,
							I am looking for a 14 to 16 week internship to put my skills into practice.
						</p>
						<p class="cv-profile-text">
							Curious and rigorous, I wish to contribute to concrete and technical projects,
							while strengthening my sense of teamwork.
						</p>
					</section>

					<section class="cv-section">
						<h2 class="cv-section-title">Contact Information</h2>
						<ul class="cv-contact-list">
							<li>
								<span class="cv-contact-icon" aria-hidden="true">
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
								</span>
